--- 
title     : BinaryIO
summary   : Read and Write Binary Data
license   : Apache 2.0
contact   : rubyworks-mailinglist@googlegroups.com
suite     : RubyWorks 
created   : 2003-01-01

authors:
  - Michael Neumann
  - Thomas Sawyer

resources:
  home: http://rubyworks.github.com/binaryio
  code: http://github.com/rubyworks/binaryio

requires:
  - redline (build)

description:
  Provides a BinaryIO class as well as a reusable mixin, BinaryIO::Readable, which
  is the heart of the BinaryIO class. The mixin solely depends one method, read(n),
  which must be defined in the class/module where the module is mixed.

